original: A lively parade filled the streets as participants marched in colorful costumes and hats. Among the crowd, one individual even sported a large plate on their head! Delighted children watched from the sidelines, clapping and expressing their joy. The parade came to a cheerful conclusion, leaving a lasting impression on all who witnessed it.
